<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-882] Condition evaluator serializers adding an empty namespace when we serialize the condition</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-882</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we add a condition to the urlrewrite mediator,, an empty namespace is added to the &amp;lt;and&amp;gt; tag automatically. &lt;br/&gt;
eg: &amp;lt;condition&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;and xmlns=&quot;&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;equal type=&quot;url&quot; source=&quot;host&quot; value=&quot;localhost&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;not&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;equal type=&quot;url&quot; source=&quot;protocol&quot; value=&quot;https&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/not&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/and&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/condition&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Added a patch for preventing the rule serilaizers to add an empty namespace when serializing the condition.&lt;br/&gt;
Please review and commit&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
